{"tid":1344593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［廣傳］迫人罷工可以用呢招","createTime":"2019-07-21T23:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T03:51:02.000Z","uid":232014,"like":593,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"c112517048b7d079247386ac5344f437b59ea3e1","tid":1344593,"uid":232014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T23:50:00.000Z","msg":"其實港鐵咁多條線<br />\n好難搵得夠人去每架車都塞住佢唔比佢運作<br />\n最直接方法一定係落路軌等佢行都冇得行<br />\n因為響應活動人數唔夠多<br />\n全部坐哂落路軌其實佢都好難逐個捉逐個趕<br />\n不過問題係有閘門既情況下點先跳到落路軌<br />\n<br />\n三月既時候其實已經有個鬼佬走左落去裸跑<br />\n成功令港鐵延誤到仆街<br />\n<br />\n【跑到出血】裸男闖路軌 由荔景奔跑到葵興<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190316/59376809\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190316%2F59376809&d=D9%2BIkncl4BF5lZ8wPV9kyCVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=8ac7b2c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190316%2F59376809&h=685695f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190316/59376809</a><br />\n<br />\n而家仲係返工時間 仲未遲架 快快手推"},{"pid":"c2f3adb8cacae0229c3895be8c2b1413972012d5","tid":1344593,"uid":232014,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T23:50:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"609af2e2c2eb13ecefe934b283949f30a794e3da","tid":1344593,"uid":232014,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T23:50:30.000Z","msg":"個個坐哂係到狗都好難趕"},{"pid":"a69e9dc3c2744b48981435dc1131e65c6002ea4e","tid":1344593,"uid":232014,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T23:50:54.000Z","msg":"唔知可唔可行 大家討論下"},{"pid":"ffa4447ed55647a61bd955ea0cc4062e3a40a410","tid":1344593,"uid":232014,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T23:51:23.000Z","msg":"邊一個位可以跳落去就講 等人知"},{"pid":"318ce3c6826acad8d57771d3c0bbf407063199ed","tid":1344593,"uid":268217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor